==English==
===Etymology===
Alteration of ''[[nyas]]'', by misanalysis of ‘a nyas’ as ‘an eyas’.

===Pronunciation===
{{IPA|/ˈaɪəs/}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun|es}}

# A young [[hawk]] or [[falcon]] in the nest, or that has not yet [[fledged]], especially one that will be trained for [[falconry]].

